decay_blend.latex:
\begin{aligned}
\alpha &= 1 - 2^{-1/h}, \; h=\text{half-life (years)}\\
R^{\text{year}}_{p,y} &\in [0,1]\; \text{(norm of current-year risk)}\\
R^{\text{cum}}_{p,y} &= (1-\alpha) \cdot R^{\text{cum}}_{p,y-1} + \alpha \cdot R^{\text{raw}}_{p,y}\\
R^{\text{cum}*}_{p,y} &\in [0,1]\; \text{(norm of }R^{\text{cum}}_{p,y}\text{)}\\
R^{\text{final}}_{p,y} &= (1-w)\,R^{\text{year}}_{p,y} + w\,R^{\text{cum}*}_{p,y},\;\; w\in[0,1]
\end{aligned}
